    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Methodology\n",
        "\n",
        "- **BERT**: Fine-tuned `bert-base-uncased` with Optuna hyperparameter optimisation on a 3-class classification head\n",
        "- **Gemma 4**: Tested with zero-shot and few-shot prompting strategies using the E2B variant\n",
        "- **Evaluation**: Accuracy, precision, recall, and F1-score (macro) across all models\n",
        "\n",
        "## Model Performance Comparison"
      ],
      "id": "8134d250"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "results = pd.DataFrame({\n",
        "    'Model': ['BERT (Optimised)', 'Gemma 4 (Zero-Shot)', 'Gemma 4 (Few-Shot)'],\n",
        "    'Accuracy': [0.8000, 0.7480, 0.6834],\n",
        "    'Precision': [0.8001, 0.7664, 0.7380],\n",
        "    'Recall': [0.8100, 0.7645, 0.7118],\n",
        "    'F1 (Macro)': [0.8040, 0.7605, 0.6725]\n",
        "}).set_index('Model')\n",
        "\n",
        "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 5))\n",
        "results.plot(kind='bar', ax=ax, colormap='Set2')\n",
        "ax.set_ylabel('Score')\n",
        "ax.set_ylim(0, 1.05)\n",
        "ax.set_xticklabels(ax.get_xticklabels(), rotation=15, ha='right')\n",
        "ax.legend(loc='lower right')\n",
        "ax.set_title('Model Performance Comparison')\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ],
      "id": "6cb4e55a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
