    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Key Findings\n",
        "\n",
        "- **BERT outperformed Gemma 4** across all metrics when fine-tuned on domain-specific data, achieving 80% accuracy vs 74.8% for Gemma zero-shot\n",
        "- **BERT was ~9x faster** for inference — 11.1ms per sample vs 101ms for Gemma 4\n",
        "- **Gemma 4 zero-shot** performed reasonably well without any training, showing strong general language understanding\n",
        "- **Few-shot prompting** did not improve over zero-shot for this task, dropping to 68.3% accuracy\n",
        "- **Error patterns** showed BERT handled nuanced neutral sentiment better, while Gemma was stronger on clearly positive/negative text"
      ],
      "id": "72dd1854"
